The Journey: Preview of new film portraying Ian Paisley and Martin McGuinness

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The world premiere of a film about the friendship forged between former political enemies Ian Paisley and Martin McGuinness takes place at the Venice Film Festival on Wednesday night.

